parameters:
Konoha-sama, have you been slurring your words
lately? I'm always available to practice
swordsmanship with you.
The castle seems a bit busy. Did something happen?

Is this my \C[1]memory\C[0]? The me before coming
here...?

It feels so nostalgic... but I can't remember...
it hurts... my head... it hurts.

Is this my \C[1]memory\C[0]? The me before coming
here...?

It feels so nostalgic... but I can't remember...
it hurts... my head... it hurts.
~The Hero of Disodart~ Priest Muramasa Rests Here

Father... Today, I was able to spend the day in
peace...

Well then, I've finished my patrol, so I guess
it's fine to stay around here today.
Lord Konoha! Excuse me! Are you here...!
What's wrong? Why are you so flustered?

An emergency situation has occurred. I can't
reveal the details unless you come to the castle.
Do you have time?

O-Okay, I understand. I'll head there right away,
so please wait for me.

It seems like something unusual is going on. Let's
hurry.
